  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Recommended update for open-vm-tools",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for open-vm-tools fixes the following issues:\n\n- update to 13.0.10 based on build 25056151 (boo#1257357):\n    * There are no new features in the open-vm-tools 13.0.10 release.\n    * This is primarily a maintenance release that addresses a fix.\n    * A minor enhancement has been made for Guest OS Customization.\n    * The DeployPkg plugin has been updated to handle a new cloud-init error code that\n      signals a recoverable error and allow cloud-init to finish running.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
